              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/26411454/" class="">第十八集</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/63126174/" class=" " title="金璃玛。">金璃玛。</a>
                (你相信他，他便是美好的。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
