              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/35376792/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/chase5/" class=" " title="Un1Amico">Un1Amico</a>
                (life&#39; s a struggle)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
